Purpose of Project:
        Finding a worker was a tough task before, but now,
        it can be done easily by this app, you can search for
        the workers according to your needs like Cooking, Washing,
        Dusting, Home Nurse, Domestic Maid Servant Services, Carpenter,
        Driver etc. The beneficial feature of this app is finding a
        specialist nearby to get service quickly and avoid mediators.

Tool:
    Django rest framework
================================================================================
FUNCTIONALITIES:
REGISTER USER:
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/registration/
    get:view all users
    post:
        sample input==>
                    {
                        "first_name": "binsha",
                        "last_name": "v",
                        "username": "binsha",
                        "password": "binsha"
                    }
        sample output==>
                {
                    "first_name": "binsha",
                    "last_name": "v",
                    "username": "binsha",
                    "password": "binsha"
                }
=============================================================================

LOGIN USER:
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/userlogin/
    post:
        sample input==>
                {
                    "username": "bakshan",
                    "password": "bakshan"
                }
        sample output==>
                {
                    "token": "0df6f4821d8051980ddc97b151b0abc417aa9b1d"
                }

LOGIN ADMIN
   url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/adminlogin/
    post:
        sample input==>
                {
                    "username": "shaneeba",
                    "password": "shaneeba"
                }
        sample output==>
                {
                    "token": "0df6f4821d8051980ddc97b151b0abc417aa9b1d"
                }

====================================================================================
LOCATION VIEW
    access:admin
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/location_view/
    get:get all locations

LOCATION CREATE
    access:admin
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/location_create/
    post:
        sample input==>
                   {

                        "dist": "palakkad",
                        "state": "kerala",
                        "country": "india"
                   }
        sample output==>
                    {

                        "dist": "palakkad",
                        "state": "kerala",
                        "country": "india"
                    }

GET A LOCATION
    access:users
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/view_a_location/1
    get: get details of a location
DELETE,UPDATE A LOCATION
    access:admin
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/change_a_location/1
    put:update a location
                {

                    "dist": "malappuram",
                    "state": "kerala",
                    "country": "india"
                }
    delete:delete a location
=========================================================================================
CREATE JOB
        access:admin
        url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/job_create/
        post:
                {
                    "job_name": "carpenter",
                    "daily_wages": 700
                }
VIEW JOBS
        access:users
        url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/job_view/
        get:get all available jobs

GET A JOB
    access:users
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/view_a_job/1
    get:get details of a job

UPDATE,DELETE A JOB
    access:admin
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/change_a_job/1
    put:update a job
    delete:delete a job

============================================================================================

CREATE A WORKER
    access:login users,admin
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/worker/
    get:details of a worker
    post:post worker

GET,UPDATE,DELETE A WORKER
    access:login users ,admin
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/worker/1
    get:get details of a worker
    update:update a worker
    delete:delete a user
===============================================================================================
SEARCH A WORKER BASED ON LOCATION,JOB,AVAILABLITY
    acess:users
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/worker/kannur
    get:details of workers

==========================================================

HIRE A WORKER
    access:users
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/hireworker/
    post:hire a worker
            {

                "worker": "Jane",
                "address": "xyz,ernakulam",
                "location": "ernakulam",
                "customer": "bakshan",
                "hire": "Hire Worker",
                "days": 1,
                "customer_phone": "123456"
            }

FEEDBACK CREATE:
    access:login users
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/feedback_create/
    post:post a feebback of worker
       sample input==>
                      {
                        "customer_name": "binsha",
                        "worker_name": "harry",
                        "feedback": "Bad",
                        "content": "not good"
                      }

FEEDBACK VIEW
    access:admin
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/feedback_view/
    get:get all feedback

COMMENT:
    access:login users,admin
    url:http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/workers/v1/comment/
    get:get all comments
    post:post a comment
                sample input==>
                      {
                        "worker": "Jane",
                        "user": "bakshan",
                        "content": "good"
                      }

